Class NumericRange<T extends Number & Comparable<?>>

    T - the type of numbers and step that are both a number and comparable
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Generator<T>, Range<T,T>

    public abstract class NumericRange<T extends Number & Comparable<?>>
extends LoopGenerator<T>
implements Range<T,T>
    A base class for numeric ranges. The elements within this range must be a Number and Comparable.
